---
layout: page.liquid
title: Projects
permalink: "/projects.html"
redirect_from: [
  "/projects/index.html",
  "/portfolio/index.html",
  "/portfolio.html",
]
---
<style>
  .projects-page {
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
  }
  .projects-page > p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .project-item {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
  .project-item-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--text-color);
  }
  .project-item-description {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .project-item-description p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .project-item-links {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
  }
  .project-item-links li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  .projects-footer {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>

<div class="projects-page">
  <p>
    I like to use free time to create fun stuff or useful things, mainly for myself, but I share them too. They might
    not even have any practical purpose.
  </p>
  <p>
    This page lists some of my projects, so you can get an idea of what I've been up to:
  </p>

  {% for project in projects %}
  <div class="project-item">
    <h2 class="project-item-title">{{ project.name }}</h2>

    <div class="project-item-description">
      {% for paragraph in project.description %}
      <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if project.links %}
    <ul class="project-item-links">
      {% for link in project.links %}
      <li><a href="{{ link.destination }}">{{ link.text }}</a></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endfor %}

  <p class="projects-footer">
    You can find all my open-source projects on <a href="https://github.com/VarunBarad" rel="me">my GitHub account</a>.
  </p>
</div>
